description:
Today, we live in a time of freedom and prosperity, when it is relatively easy to serve God. If we cannot follow God during these times of ease, then it is unlikely that we will decide to follow Him when we lose our freedoms and face challenges and difficulties. How important is it that we always be true and faithful to God, regardless of the circumstances around us?
